LAHORE, May 11 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has approved recommendations of the cabinet committee for corona to vaccinate the media persons across the province.
In this regard, the CM said media persons would be vaccinated on priority basis after Eid and asked the health department to take necessary steps and setting up of vaccination centres in press clubs be reviewed.
